 were gone like hotcakes within 8 hours of putting my merchant up).  Apparently they're for some Ranger quest (ironic eh? A mage sticking it to another class on drops?  hehe please forgive me, Quillmane has sunk into my soul <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).<br>
